-page_head__ttl -white\">社員の声</h1>\n\t\t\n\t</div>\n</div></div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_module_1698327624531\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n\n<section class=\"p-section -default\">\n  \n  \n  <div class=\"p-section__body\">\n    \n    <div class=\"l-inner-wide-pc l-inner-default-sp\">\n    \n      <div class=\"c-custom_html\">\n        <div class=\"addcg-project_story\"><br>\n<ul>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.change-jp.com/recruit/voicesofourteam/01\" rel=\"noopener\" linktext=\"キャリア採用社員に聞く。チェンジの仕事の魅力とは\n\n人材育成\nIT・DX支援\n座談会\n中途社員\"> <img src=\"https://www.change-jp.com/hubfs/img_voice_01.jpg\" alt=\"img_voice_01\">\n<p>キャリア採用社員に聞く。チェンジの仕事の魅力とは</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">人材育成</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">IT・DX支援</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">座談会</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">中途社員</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/voicesofourteam/02\"> <img src=\"https://www.change-jp.com/hubfs/Group%20624935.jpg\" alt=\"img_voice_02\">\n<p>新卒社員から社長に抜擢。第二創業期を迎えるチェンジの魅力</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">代表インタビュー</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">事業を創る</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">新卒入社</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/voicesofourteam/03\"> <img src=\"https://www.change-jp.com/hubfs/%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%E6%9C%AA%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E3%81%AE%E3%83%87%E3%82%B6%E3%82%A4%E3%83%B3%20(12).png\" alt=\"img_voice_03\">\n<p>「あの時代にチェンジっていう会社があったから今がある」 そういわれる未来を目指して</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">代表インタビュー</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">今後の展望</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">中途社員向け</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/voicesofourteam/04\" linktext=\"挑戦できるから、成長できる。\n若手が語る「チェンジ」のリアル。\n\n新卒入社\n座談会\n就活\n人材育成\nIT・DX支援\"> <img src=\"https://www.change-jp.com/hubfs/HP%E5%85%A8%E4%BD%93%E6%8E%B2%E8%BC%89%E5%86%99%E7%9C%9F%20(1).png\" alt=\"img_voice_04\">\n<p>挑戦できるから、成長できる。 <br>若手が語る「チェンジ」のリアル。</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">新卒入社</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">座談会</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">就活</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">人材育成</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">IT・DX支援</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/voicesofourteam/05\" linktext=\"「『失敗の次』が本当の勝負」と信じ\n臆することなくチャレンジを続ける。\n\n新卒入社\n新規事業開発\n最年少マネージャー\"> <img src=\"https://www.change-jp.com/hubfs/44116915/HP%E5%85%A8%E4%BD%93%E6%8E%B2%E8%BC%89%E5%86%99%E7%9C%9F%20(2).png\" alt=\"img_voice_05\">\n<p>「『失敗の次』が本当の勝負」と信じ <br>臆することなくチャレンジを続ける。</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">新卒入社</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">新規事業開発</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">最年少マネージャー</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/voicesofourteam/06\" linktext=\"人材育成を得意とするチェンジ。新卒入社社員が語る、新入社員研修のリアルとは\n\n新卒入社\n新規事業開発\n最年少マネージャー\"> <img src=\"https://www.change-jp.com/hubfs/%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%A7%E7%94%BB%E9%9D%A2.png\" alt=\"img_voice_06\">\n<p>人材育成を得意とするチェンジ<br>新卒入社社員が語る、新入社員研修のリアルとは</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">新卒入社</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">新卒研修</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">人材育成</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">新規事業開発</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">IT・DX支援</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.change-jp.com/recruit/voicesofourteam/voicesofourteam/07\" rel=\"noopener\" linktext=\"家庭と仕事を両立しながらキャリアは止めない。\n\nワーパパ\n仕事と家庭の両立\n人材育成\n事業推進\nIT・DX支援\"> <img src=\"https://www.change-jp.com/hubfs/%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%A7%E7%94%BB%E9%9D%A2%20(2).png\" alt=\"img_voice_07\">\n<p>家庭と仕事を両立しながらキャリアは止めない。</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">ワーパパ</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">仕事と家庭の両立</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">人材育成</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">事業推進</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">IT・DX支援</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n<a href=\"voicesofourteam/07\"> </a><a href=\"voicesofourteam/07\"> </a></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  \n</section></div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"foot-contents\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container-fluid\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_widget_1698300049887\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\"><div class=\"p-bread\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"l-inner-default-pc l-inner-default-sp\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"p-bread__row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"p-bread__item\"><a href=\"https://www.change-jp.com/recruit/\" class=\"p-bread__link\">TOP</a><span class=\"u-dn-sp\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"u-dn-sp\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&n